description: Attention investors! Welcome to 11 Dexter, a beautifully gut renovated 5-bedroom, 4-bath single-family with 2,200 sq. ft., two parking spaces, and outdoor space. Completely gutted to the studs in 2022, everything is brand new including central air, heat, and high-end finishes. Beyond the home itself, the location is unmatched—just steps to the Red Line and directly beside the highly anticipated On the Dot project, poised to transform the neighborhood with new businesses, residences, and lifestyle amenities. This proximity positions the property for exceptional long-term appreciation and growth. Currently rented for $6,700/month through 8/31/26, it offers immediate cash flow for investors.
